title: DAKINE Super-Grab Contest with Windells
description:
During the glorious summer months on Mt. Hood, DAKINE and the Windell's Camp teamed up to create the DAKINE Super-Grab contest, supported by Gore-Tex. All the winners won a ticket for a free pair of DAKINE Gore-tex gloves!
Check out the highlights from one of this summer's events!
